## Step 1: Create NUnit Test Project

Create a new NUnit test project for your integration tests:

```bash
dotnet new nunit -n YourService.IntegrationTests
```

**Project Structure Recommendation:**
```
YourService.IntegrationTests/
├── Constants/
├── Extensions/
├── Helpers/
├── Tests/
├── appsettings.json
└── YourService.IntegrationTests.csproj
```

